snippet.title: Arctic Empire
snippet.description:
Saving the world one track at a time! 
Melodic dubstep, chillstep and future bass enthusiast. 

Submit music and artwork here: https://arcticempire.edmdistrict.com
Labels & managers can contact me at arcticempire@outlook.com
If you have a question about the channel just send a message on Instagram.

FAQ
Q: Can I use the tracks posted on Arctic Empire on my youtube/twitch channel?
A: It's not up to me to answer that, you need to ask the producer for permission to use their music.

Thanks for checking out the channel,
Nelson
